HEADWORD: Slavocracy
<hw>Slav*oc"ra*cy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Slave</ets> + <ets>-cracy</ets>, as in
<ets>democracy</ets>.]</ety> <def>The persons or interest formerly
